      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JAYASHREE (5) got the job done narrowly two back before a strong performance in defeat over 1625m last time out. Faithfull rides now and she'll be fitter again now. Jumped a $1.55 favourite last time out and she looks the one to beat if she can run to recent form. MONTY ZOOMER (1) dropped back in trip last start and was strong, despite finishing 1L off the winner. Back out to a more suitable trip now where he's won 2/3. Li's claim is a big tick and he'll take plenty of beating with his racing pattern. RIVERCREST MAGIC (8) got the job done in a photo two back before getting well back and not featuring when back in trip last start. This shapes similarly to her win  a couple of starts back and the inside draw this time is a big tick. Can sit handier and return to winning ways. PLEASE MIZTER (6) can put his best foot forward back to his preferred track and trip. SO MANY STORIES (9) is racing well and can't be left out of calculations.",
